  "body": "It'd be great to have automatic discovery of ingress resources based on annotations like for services, pods, endpoints, etc. for blackbox checks and similar:\r\n\r\n```\r\n---\r\napiVersion: extensions/v1beta1\r\nkind: Ingress\r\nmetadata:\r\n  name: myservice\r\n  annotations:\r\n    prometheus.io/probe: 'true'\r\n    prometheus.io/module: http_4xx_ssl\r\nspec:\r\n  tls:\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\nRight now ingress doesn't seem to be implemented yet at all.",
